#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Traceability Matching:</b> The system intelligently filters \"Convert "
"Into\" options based on tracing. For example, if you convert a Lot-tracked "
"item and provide a new Lot number, the destination product must also support "
"Lot tracking. But if you dont provide any Lot Number, only product without "
"specific traceability will be eligible for convert into."
msgstr ""

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
