"簡単です!"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"これはパッケージに含まれる機能の概要にすぎません。新しいアプリを追加したり、"
"デモデータを削除/変更したり、自由にテストしてみましょう!"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"On the finished product's settings, you'll need to add the subcontractor to "
"the <b>vendor list</b>. Be sure to include the price you'll pay for their "
"subcontracting service."
msgstr ""
"プロダクトの設定において、下請業者を<b>仕入先リスト</b> に追加する必要があり"
"ます。下請けサービスに対して支払う価格を必ず含めてください。"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once clicking on \"Convert\" button an <b>Automated Manufacturing Order "
"(MO)</b> is executed in the background:"
msgstr ""

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once production is planned, workers can execute and monitor their tasks "
"using the <b>Shop Floor App</b>. This app can be installed as a standalone "
"application. It's designed to be used by multiple employees on a single "
"device, with each\n"
"            employee registering their work individually."
msgstr ""

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once production orders are confirmed, they need to be planned. The scheduled "
"date on the <b>Manufacturing Order (MO)</b> is just an initial estimate and "
"doesn't consider your actual capacity."
msgstr ""
"製造オーダが確定したら、次に計画を立てる必要があります。<b>製造オーダ(MO)</"
"b> に表示される予定日はあくまで初期の見積りであり、実際の生産能力は考慮されて"
"いません。"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
